reviewText: House Of Payne - Volume One, Episodes 1-20Tyler Perry's House of Payne, Vol. 2: Episodes 21-40 My View of the DVDs are Outstanding. I'am waiting for Volume 3 episodes 41 and so on. I have everything Tyler and will continue buying everything of tyler perry.

I HAVE BOTH VOL.1 AND 2. AND I ENJOY THEM BOTH. WHEN EVER I FEEL LIKE HAVING A GOOD LAUGH, I JUST PUT ON ONE OF THESE DVD'S.
Once again Tyler Perry comes through with hilarious family fun!  You just can't miss any episodes.
